svg.text: Read Jessie’s e-mail. Which is her bed?
Hi, Thomas! I love my new house! My sister and I have a big bedroom. Everything is pink and
purple! There is big window and there’s a small closet next to my sister’s bed. We have clothes
and shoes in it. There is a long rug between the beds. There is a night table, with a drawer and a
lamp on it. And under the drawer I have my photo
album. There is a mirror on the wall. There isn’t a
above my bed. There are cushions on the beds
because I don’t have a bookshelf. There are beds
under the beds! Look at the photo.
